{
  "type": "excalidraw",
  "version": 2,
  "source": "claude-code",
  "elements": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t1",
      "x": 150,
      "y": 20,
      "text": "Decision 2: Split Redis into 2 Clusters",
      "fontSize": 24,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t2",
      "x": 150,
      "y": 55,
      "text": "Problem: One Redis holds everything \u2014 if it dies, the entire platform goes down.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#c92a2a"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t3",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 100,
      "text": "BEFORE \u2014 Single Redis Instance",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "strokeColor": "#c92a2a"
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "r4",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 130,
      "width": 620,
      "height": 253,
      "backgroundColor": "#ffe3e3",
      "strokeColor": "#c92a2a",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t5",
      "x": 66,
      "y": 144,
      "text": "ONE Redis Instance Holds EVERYTHING:\n\n\u2022 Live tick snapshots (FEED_PP_*)\n\u2022 OHLC, previous close, circuit limits, 52-week H/L\n\u2022 Chart candles (current-day)\n\u2022 FNO option chain + Greeks + insights\n\u2022 Market movers sorted sets\n\u2022 Trading day status flag\n\n\u2192 If this Redis dies (AWS Multi-AZ failover: 15-30 sec)\n\u2192 FULL PLATFORM OUTAGE:\n    \u2717 Feed pipeline stops writing\n    \u2717 Charts API returns errors\n    \u2717 FNO API returns errors\n    \u2717 Market Movers API returns errors\n    \u2717 WebSocket shows frozen prices",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "strokeColor": "#c92a2a"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t6",
      "x": 740,
      "y": 100,
      "text": "AFTER \u2014 Two Independent Clusters",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44"
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "r7",
      "x": 740,
      "y": 130,
      "width": 620,
      "height": 154,
      "backgroundColor": "#d0ebff",
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t8",
      "x": 756,
      "y": 144,
      "text": "REDIS CLUSTER 1  (Feed Pipeline)\n\n\u2022 Live tick snapshots (FEED_PP_*)\n\u2022 OHLC, previous close, circuit limits\n\u2022 52-week H/L, trading day status\n\nWriters: Publisher (via Lua atomic scripts)\nReaders: Periscope API, Broadcast Service\n          (for snapshot-on-connect)",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2"
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "r9",
      "x": 740,
      "y": 304,
      "width": 620,
      "height": 182,
      "backgroundColor": "#d3f9d8",
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t10",
      "x": 756,
      "y": 318,
      "text": "REDIS CLUSTER 2  (API Read Cache)\n\n\u2022 Current-day chart candles ({pmlId}_{date})\n\u2022 FNO option chain hashes per expiry\n\u2022 Option insights (PCR, Max Pain, ATM Straddle)\n\u2022 Market movers sorted sets\n\nWriters: Charts Data Writer, FNO Data Writer,\n          Market Movers Writer\nReaders: Charts API, FNO Dashboard API,\n          Market Movers API",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t11",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 526,
      "text": "Failure Scenarios Compared",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e"
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "r12",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 556,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 112,
      "backgroundColor": "#d0ebff",
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t13",
      "x": 66,
      "y": 570,
      "text": "If Redis Cluster 1 dies:\n\u2713 Live price writes pause for 15-30 sec\n\u2713 Kafka keeps flowing (no tick loss)\n\u2713 Charts / FNO / Movers APIs keep serving\n\u2713 WebSocket delivery continues (Kafka-based)\n\u2717 Snapshot-on-connect unavailable until recovery",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2"
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "r14",
      "x": 510,
      "y": 556,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 112,
      "backgroundColor": "#d3f9d8",
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t15",
      "x": 526,
      "y": 570,
      "text": "If Redis Cluster 2 dies:\n\u2713 Feed pipeline fully unaffected\n\u2713 Kafka keeps flowing to Broadcast\n\u2713 WebSocket users still see live prices\n\u2717 Charts API returns errors (15-30 sec)\n\u2717 FNO + Movers APIs return errors (15-30 sec)",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44"
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "r16",
      "x": 970,
      "y": 556,
      "width": 400,
      "height": 140,
      "backgroundColor": "#fff9db",
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t17",
      "x": 986,
      "y": 570,
      "text": "If BOTH die (rare):\n\u2717 Full outage until recovery\n\nBUT Kafka still persists all ticks\n\u2192 On recovery, replay last N seconds\n\u2192 Zero permanent data loss\n\nMulti-AZ with separate AZ placement",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00"
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "r18",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 726,
      "width": 1320,
      "height": 62,
      "backgroundColor": "#fff9db",
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t19",
      "x": 66,
      "y": 742,
      "text": "Cost:  ~$200/month extra for 2nd ElastiCache instance.  Config: maxmemory-policy = noeviction, alert at 80% usage.\nUse key prefixes (no DB 5/6/7 pattern) \u2014 required for future Redis Cluster migration.  Neither failure kills everything.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00"
    }
  ],
  "appState": {
    "gridSize": null,
    "viewBackgroundColor": "#ffffff"
  }
}